thread.title: Several killed in bridge collapse at Florida college

title: Several killed in bridge collapse at Florida college
text:
Several killed in bridge collapse at Florida college 7:21pm GMT - 00:31 
A pedestrian bridge has collapsed at Florida International University in western Miami Dade County, trapping cars and killing several people. Linda So reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
